# Power BI MIS Dashboard

## Overview
This dashboard is a Power BI version of the Excel MIS project, built to demonstrate data modeling, DAX calculations, and interactive business dashboards.

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Power BI
- Power Query
- DAX
- Data Modeling

## Key Features
- Data transformation using Power Query
- Relationship based data model
- KPI cards and business metrics
- Interactive filters and slicers
- Order and delivery performance analysis

## Dashboard Insights
The Power BI dashboard provides insights on:
- Total Orders
- On-time vs Delayed deliveries
- SLA performance
- Monthly order trends
- Operational efficiency

## Purpose
This project demonstrates how operational data can be transformed into an interactive BI dashboard for decision making.
